Vulnerability -> Trust -> Conflict -> Commitment -> Accountability


1. Vulnerability-based trust: vulnerability is important (https://www.ted.com/talks/brene_brown_the_power_of_vulnerability)
2. Overcom fear of conflict: trust + conflict = pursue of truth;
  - conflict is necessary


How to build trust? Know one another


Virtual work:
1. Keep video and audio on
2. Engage in a call chat (show appreciation)

How to integrate a person in a team: ask new person questions and answer the questions themselves.

Sources:
Patrick Lencioni's talk (24.06.2020)
